[34m│[0m Some backends might return all users' data.                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### IDOR Bypass Techniques                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HTTP Method Change:**                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Change `POST → PUT` or `GET → POST`                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Some endpoints have different authorization checks                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Content Type Change:**                                                     [34m│[0m
