[34m│[0m    ↓ blocked?                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 7. TRY COMPOUND MUTATIONS                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Combine 2-3 techniques from above                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - E.g., double-encode + case + fragmentation                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
