[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Parameter Pollution:**                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m user_id=hacker_id&user_id=victim_id                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Some applications use first value, others use last, some combine.            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Testing Workflow                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 1. **Identify Object References:**                                           [34m│[0m
